WEBVTT

00:03.000 --> 00:13.000
BURN NOTICE: THE FALL OF SAM AXE (2011)

00:13.002 --> 00:17.000
Burn Notice: The Fall of Sam Axe
Original Air Date on April 17, 2011

00:19.000 --> 00:25.074
